00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,160
Kakek, sudah sampai di rumah sakit.

93
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,720
Qiao Dan, gendong dia.

94
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:51,640
Bukankah itu rekan Long Qi, Yu Daluo?

95
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:54,120
Tidak mungkin.

96
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:56,360
Kau lihat yang jelas,
dia turun dari mobil polisi.

97
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:58,360
Pelan-pelan.

98
00:09:01,560 --> 00:09:02,960
Dorong.

99
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,320
Apa yang kau lihat?

100
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,360
Rasanya sedikit familier.

101
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:11,840
- Halo.
- Kebetulan sekali, Gu Linna.

102
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,960
