00:09:14,800 --> 00:09:16,080
Benar sekali.

104
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:20,720
Kau tidak perlu menganggap serius
masalah kemarin, itu hanya hal biasa.

105
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:22,360
Di mana Long Qi?

106
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:25,480
Bukankah kemarin kalian masih bersama?

107
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:30,880
Dia itu Longji, Yu Longji, adikku.

108
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:35,600
Sebentar, apakah bukan dia?

109
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:43,520
Mohon tunjukkan
kartu identitas kalian kepadaku.

110
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:45,480
Ada apa?

111
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:47,280
Prosedur kepolisian.

112
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,040
Sebentar.

113
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:51,480
Apakah kau yakin bahwa dirimu
bukan teman dari buronan itu?

114
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:54,760
Kenapa seorang buronan
menemui kalian di tempat parkir?

115
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:56,560
Apakah ada buronan yang imut sepertiku?

116
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:57,920
Kartu identitas.

117
00:09:58,920 --> 00:09:59,560
Baiklah.

118
00:10:06,620 --> 00:10:09,040
(Hong Zinuo, Linna)

119
00:10:09,040 --> 00:10:11,640
Mohon kerja sama kalian
untuk ikut denganku.

120
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,480
Pak Yu, apa yang sebenarnya terjadi?

121
00:10:15,880 --> 00:10:17,280
Nona Gu, begini.

122
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:19,680
Agar tidak ada masalah yang melibatkan
salah satu dari kita,

123
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:21,480
